                            <a href="https://github.com/vvgonline" target="_blank"><span
                                    class="badge badge-secondary">build</span></a> exciting stuff.
                        </p>
                    </article>
                    @* I MARKET PRODUCTS & SERVICES ONLINE 🛒 *@
                    <article>
                        <h2>
                            I <b class="prime-yellow">Market</b> products & services online 🛒
                        </h2>
                        <p>
                            To make your products / services visible and get the desired reach, I provide
                            consultancy on market research (the selection &amp; analysis of the target
                            audience), Marketplace promotion, Content Marketing (Technical documentation,
                            blogging &amp; website content) &amp; Analytics services (mobile app analytics,
                            basic web analytics, e-commerce analytics)
