                            Arranged and conducted number of College (Graduation and Post-Graduation level) /
                            Corporate trainings on MS Excel / PowerPoint / SharePoint / MS Project at Cipla /
                            Bridgestone / ManForce / Dolphine Hospital, .Net (C# / Asp), C / C++, PHP [MRSC], MY
                            SQL [MRSC], Oracle, Full Stack Development, OOAD with UML, Computer Graphics, 2D
                            animation and interactivity with Adobe Flash, UI Design with Adobe Photoshop /
                            Illustrator, How to use Selenium for testing, Manual Testing and many more.
